Scenario:
A shop offers a discount for customers who spend more than RM100.
If total purchase is greater than 100, display:
"You get a discount!"
total_spend=float(input("Enter you total spend:"))
if total_spend > 100:
    print("You get a discount!")
else:
    print("NO DISCOUNT")
